    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a migraine? i guess maybe. it was just so sudden though, i've never really had one like that before. and the foggy feeling is still kinda lingering. do you think a high dose of ibuprofen would work better than aspirin? i have some extra strength stuff here, should i just take a few of those to make sure it goes away?",
